text: 6- The average Arkansan is a lot like Mum & Tut. We’re a state of hard workers who need those same protections & benefits that allowed a Serbian coal-miner, farmer, & tavern-owner to provide for their children & grandchildren.
name: Denise Garner
description: Retired Oncology Nurse, nonprofit founder, mother & grandma. Representative for Arkansas District 84. #Denisefor84

text: 5- From the factory to the farm to the classroom—all Arkansans want is FAIRNESS. Every hard-working Arkansan deserves workplace safety, & a life where they can enjoy the benefits of their labor. Every Arkansan deserves a living wage & quality affordable health care.
name: Denise Garner
description: Retired Oncology Nurse, nonprofit founder, mother & grandma. Representative for Arkansas District 84. #Denisefor84

text:
4- This Labor Day, Hershey & I are thinking about Mum & Tut. How they came here as immigrants & worked hard to give their kids a better life. How everything could’ve been lost w/out the support of the union. 

Our story, like so many, traces back to immigration & organized labor
name: Denise Garner
description: Retired Oncology Nurse, nonprofit founder, mother & grandma. Representative for Arkansas District 84. #Denisefor84

text: 3- Tut died early from black lung. But he was a member of the United Mine Workers Union, so his family had help with medical bills & support for Mum & the kids after he was gone.
name: Denise Garner
description: Retired Oncology Nurse, nonprofit founder, mother & grandma. Representative for Arkansas District 84. #Denisefor84

text: 2- Mum ran the tavern for 18 hrs a day to cover all three shift changes at the mill. She ran the tavern & the farm with the help of five kids who pitched in before & after school.
name: Denise Garner
description: Retired Oncology Nurse, nonprofit founder, mother & grandma. Representative for Arkansas District 84. #Denisefor84

text:
1- Hershey’s grandparents Mary & George—Mum & Tut, to the grandkids—were Serbian immigrants who came to America in the 1910s.

name: Denise Garner
